LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Hey %r%... uh... like, if you wanted to break up with someone, how would you do it?

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: %random(What do you mean?,Why would you ask me something like that?,Are you trying to tell me something?)%

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: No! Uh... I mean... I have like a friend who... uh....
%r%! %r%! Guess what! I got tickets to the %toc1% festival this weekend! Just you, me, and %toc1%s everywhere!

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Are you joking? You KNOW I HATE %toc1%s!

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Come on! Give the festival a chance! We can do it together!

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: I'd rather go to %pejorative%-palooza.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Hey %sweetie%! I wrote that recommendation thing on your profile like you asked.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Really! I'll go look at it right now.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: I said you were a pretty okay %gender(r,gent,lady)%.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Pretty okay? r u serious? Just pretty okay? %random(Do you like HATE me or something?,You didn't say I was the BEST you've ever dated?)%

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: What? No, I...

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Your %random(FACE,MOM)% is pretty okay!

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Hey %r%... there's, uh, something you should know about me.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: What's that, %sweetie%?

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: I kind of like to keep my options open, dating-wise. If you know what I mean. %random(I'm like a free bird that can't be caged,I'm like a lion always on the prowl,I'm like a tomcat prowling the streets at night,I'm like a crab that has to keep looking for new shells)%.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Thanks for telling me, %i%. I appreciate your honesty. %random(I KNOW someone as honest as you would never cheat on me,I'll just have to try EXTRA hard to keep you with me)%.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: %r%... I have something to tell you.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: What is it, %sweetie%?

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: You complete me.
Yeah... I always felt like I needed some flaws to be more well-rounded.
Hey %r%... I feel like you should know that... uh... %random(I have mono,I have lice,I have chicken pox,I have irritable bowel syndrome,I have a tapeworm,I have hamster rabies)%.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Really? Oh my god get out. Me too!
We're so alike! Now we can cuddle together even more and not have to worry.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: %greeting%. Hey, uh, I was thinking... you shouldn't date me. I'm a seriously flawed individual.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: That's okay, %i%. It's why I like you.
You bet.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: %greeting%. Hey, uh, I was thinking... you shouldn't date me. I'm a seriously flawed individual.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: That's okay, %i%. I'm not perfect either. Maybe we're meant for each other.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: You think?

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Never know.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Hey %r%... uh, I was thinking... instead of going out tonight, maybe we should stay in. And read. Quietly, to ourselves.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: You're joking, right? I've totally been looking forward to going out dancing and partying!

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Oh, no. No dance. No party. Just a good, quiet night in. Maybe later if we're feeling adventurous, %random(we could read in a different room,we could move to the basement,we could switch from fiction to non-fiction,we could swap books,we could each read a line out loud,we could write reviews for my blog)%!

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: You do that, %i%. You do that. By yourself.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Hey %r%! Hey %r%! Guess what I've got planned for tonight? We're going to dancing, then to like three different parties, then skinny dipping in the lake! Oh, then karaoke!

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: What? Like out in public? No... I was just going to stay home tonight. %random(Maybe open a window or two,Maybe make some toaster pastries,Maybe have some toast and a nice glass of milk,Maybe call my grandma,Maybe rake my zen garden,Maybe install a new screensaver,Maybe play a board game. Single player)%.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: That... sounds... boring.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: I know. I'm... I'm too boring for you.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: %r%! %r%! Guess what! I got a ticket to the %toc1% festival this weekend! It's going to be soooo awesome!

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: *A* ticket? You didn't get one for me?

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Oh, uh... %random(I couldn't afford another one,I didn't think you'd want to come,I got the very last one,it's kind of a thing my friends and I are doing together,I guess I forgot)%, %sweetie%.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: I freaking LOVE %toc1%s. How could you do this to me? I'm seriously so pissed off.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Sup. Woah, you look terrible.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: I do?!
Oh, no. Thanks for letting me know, %sweetie%.

Instantiation.name: TurnOff - Responder is Dominating, won't have any of that.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: There's something different about you %r%...

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Is it my stunningly good looks?

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: No, I think you gained some weight.
Just putting it out there.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Oh no you didn't! I expect you to apologize for that and compliment me NOW!

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Uhh... yes %gender(r,sir,ma'am)%. You look amazing.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: That's better.

Instantiation.name: TurnOff - I talks about Rs friend.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Hey %sweetie%. What's your friend %o% doing later today?

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: I don't know, why do you ask?

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Oh, I don't know. I was just wondering what it would be like to be dating %pron(o,him/her)% instead of you.
Do you ever do that, %r%? Do those crazy thought experiments?
Do you think %o% and I are into the same music? I bet we are! We could listen to it together, maybe on the beach or something.
Oh, now I have to find out about the music. Catch you later, %r%!

Instantiation.name: TurnOff - Initiator rise to popularity causes issues.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Oh, hey %r%.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: %greeting% %sweetie%. Aren't we just the best couple ever?

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Ummm, yeah. I meant to talk to you about that...

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: What is it?

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Well, now that I'm becoming more popular, popular, I don't think this is going to work out. I have an image to maintain.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: That's just lame. How could you just turn your back on me like that now that you're popular?

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Look sweetie, I didn't make the rules, I just have to play the game. Unless you start improving your social image stat, I don't think we have much of a future.
Hey %r%. There's something you should know.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Was it about how totally awesome we are together?

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Actually, no. %toc1%.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Oh well, that's not so bad. I can live with it.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: But... aren't you turned off?

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Now you're just being silly. I would like you no matter what you do.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Hey %r%.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: %greeting% %sweetie%, what's up?

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: I was thinking, we should stop being friends.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Why would we want to do that?

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Well that way we can focus on just dating. You know, do more girlfriend-boyfriend stuff.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Oh... Well I guess if it will help us be an even better couple and get closer then what could go wrong?

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Ummm yeah, right, better couple and stuff. That's it.
Perfect! One more step done in sabotaging our whole relationship.

Instantiation.name: TurnOff - Other person hits on initiator

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Hey %r%, what's up.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: I was just thinking how awesome we are together.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Yeah... oh, %greeting%, %o%!

LineOfDialogue.otherLine: You sure are looking like a %positiveadj% cat, %i%!

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: You're the cat, tiger. You can check me out any time.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: You're unbelievable!
Hey %sweetie%. What's up?

LineOfDialogue.otherLine: Look, what %pron(i,he/she)% is trying to say is that you aren't good enough for %pron(o, him/her)%.
And also you are a meh %gender(r,girlfriend,boyfriend)%. I would be much better.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Is this true?

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Uhhh... awkward...
